---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Garden and its Facilities — Mas du Chanoine" description="Discover the 2500m² Mediterranean garden of Mas du Chanoine: fruit trees, rosebushes, patio, water lily pond and bowling pitch." lang="en">
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-950/70 via-primary-950/30 to-primary-950/10 z-10"></div>
    <img src="/media/jardin/fleuri.jpg" alt="The flowering Mediterranean garden of Mas du Chanoine" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
    <div class="relative z-20 text-white px-4 md:px-8 pb-12 max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-3 text-primary-200 font-light">2,500 m² of greenery</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-semibold leading-tight">Garden and its Facilities</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Mediterranean</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Garden & Fruit Trees</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>This historic farmhouse is surrounded by a flat Mediterranean garden of 2500 m² where regional vegetation abounds. On the fruit side, you will find, depending on the season, sweet or bitter oranges, lemons, grapefruit, persimmons, figs, cherry-plums, tangerines, apricots, raspberries...</p><p>Enough to offer you a wide variety of jams for breakfast!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Flowers & Scents</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Flower Beds & Rosebushes</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Numerous flower beds line the walkways around the house, as well as the small paths through the garden. More than 15 varieties of roses flower continuously.</p><p>Numerous species of Provençal flowers and shrubs adorn the various beds, in particular the lavender with its delicate scent.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Heart of the Mas</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Patio & Breakfast</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Every morning, in the patio area during breakfast you will see roses blossoming through the arches and can admire the bougainvillea hanging on the facade. It is the welcome area and the perfect place for a bit of reading or idleness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Romance</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Fish & Water Lilies</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>Refuge for a large family of goldfish, the pond is a relaxing place for a romantic moment, to admire the yellow, pink and white water lilies, and to be lulled by the gentle hiss of the fountain.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent-600 mb-3 font-medium">Leisure</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-6 text-primary-900 leading-tight">Bowling Pitch & Petanque</h2>
        <div class="prose-content text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>The bowling pitch will welcome you in the shade, under the branches of the acacias and the jacaranda. The challenge of pétanque awaits you where you will be initiated to this game of 'boules' very renowned in the French Riviera.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad bg-primary-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">Enjoy the Mediterranean garden</h2>
      <p class="text-primary-300 mb-8 text-lg">Book your stay at Mas du Chanoine.</p>
      <a href="https://masduchanoine.thais-hotel.com/hotel/website/reservations.php?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-100">Book now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
